sentences.english: Any emulator instance can act as a virtual Frame - Relay switch.
sentences.chinese: 任何仿真例程都可以表現爲一個虛擬幀中繼交換機。

sentences.english: This paper discusses an implementation of frame relay for a middle-scale router.
sentences.chinese: 文章介紹了一個在中檔路由器中的幀中繼協議的實現。

sentences.english: Increase for frame relay services remains strong although ATM technology is under rapid development.
sentences.chinese: 幀中繼業務增長的勢頭並未因ATM的發展而減弱。

sentences.english: This paper includes two parts on technology and realization of frame relay network.
sentences.chinese: 本文分兩部份研究了幀中繼網絡技術及實現。
